We can use this to search for documents with orgmode in a keyword or title too.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class="org-src-container"&gt;
&lt;pre class="src src-python"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #0000FF;"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; pymongo
